Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,木漏れ日みたいで、いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空 雲 果てしない道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっちゃい存在同士 手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと 壮大 夢見てもいいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて 寛大な 地球だい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう、きっと特別な双眼鏡だって、ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,探した景色は見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,世界で一番の絶景ポイントは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも目の前の“その笑顔”だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう いつもとなりにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう何もいらなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なかなか素直に言えないこの気持ちあふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日もコハルビヨリだ いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一句「谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就像掠过树梢的阳光 赞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝天 白云 漫漫长路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,同样渺小的存在 只要手牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就能心怀更壮大的梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球多么宽大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就算特制的望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,也找不到心中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因为世界上最棒的景点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就是时刻绽放在眼前的那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你陪伴我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,有你相伴 别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,充满心中的这份心情 总是说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是暖和的小阳春 赞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:29.68,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}翻译：dgwxx／其他：cunhan
Comment: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 在谷川岳Base Plaza乘缆车到天神平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再换乘吊椅缆车到天神岭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吊箱缆车加吊椅缆车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了攀登回忆中的谷川岳可是必经之路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道理我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但说什么都是怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是真害怕高处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 我有个想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也去山以外的地方玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在日向的提议下 大家一起出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.36,title,NTP,0,0,0,,高处 不怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临武藏丘陵森林公园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说有65个东京巨蛋那么大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公园里还有巴士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多游乐设施呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天可是转不完的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟嘿哟嘿 埼玉海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海盗啊 海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的们 起锚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学之后就没玩过滑梯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵来来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么矮总没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 一点没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个高度没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学之后还是第一次荡秋千呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫学姐 我们踢鞋玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看谁沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 日向你比较重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比你高 重是自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才差3厘米而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差3厘米也是我高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说体重呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱 好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股好烫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐不滑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑自行车也很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古镰仓街道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有历史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古人从这一路走到镰仓 小田原呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:22.99,yama_neta,NTP,0,0,0,,镰仓 小田原 位于神奈川县 距武藏丘陵森林公园约110公里（现代国道）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古人真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爬个富士山就累趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 鸟窝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有没有鼯鼠或者白颊鼯鼠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边倒是有松鼠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱 拿着竹叶干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把竹叶啊 这样折过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是竹叶船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹叶还能这么玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就开始午餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿瘪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都拿来了吗 自制便当！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经说好大家各自准备便当了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让用脱水食材 可真为难我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先从小葵开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的便当是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好精致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晨五点起床做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一副了不起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是可可娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主题是妖精的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得甜食也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晨六点起来做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 种类丰富真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛从刚才就一副了不起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是小枫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…那个 你们别笑话我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是梅子 这个是鲣鱼 还有金枪鱼和海带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺激食欲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野性也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这了不起的样子是搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该你了 快给我们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼 想看？ 想看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法 无论如何都想看的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个肯定不是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸早晨三点起床给我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可起劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫起劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晨三点 还是半夜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:07:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫学姐 鲣鱼饭团子真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 炸鸡块给我好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱桃番茄好甜 真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 大家一起在大自然里吃饭 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 吃过饭有个想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想 想去的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吊桥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没多高的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怎么摇晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前看 别慌 慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是担心我害怕缆车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我习惯高处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才带我来这个公园？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这家伙其实很会关心人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 过来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵学姐 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 日向 谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就是嘭嘭山！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘭嘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没长大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面怪高的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再稍微往上面一点吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚才的小山弹力大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼 玩疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你 这不是不怕高了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 一点都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为玩得高兴 还是因为沉浸其中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还是害怕高处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有日向和大家 无论是吊箱还是吊椅 都能战胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 一加一等于？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的口号是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:04.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,晴れた日も 雨の日も しあわせだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:07.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,天気予報はいらないね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:12.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,また明日 あたらしい 空に描こう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:16.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,消えない Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:27.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,紙と色鉛筆だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:30.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな夢も叶えられた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:34.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,子供の頃の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,取り戻したような日々
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:47.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しかった季節ひとつが終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:55.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,まっしろなスケジュール 落書きで埋めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,12色パレットじゃ描けない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:04.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心に焼きついてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,好きなひと100人にいつか見せたい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:12.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,花咲くアシアト
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,晴れた日も 雨の日も しあわせだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,天気予報はいらないね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,軽やかに 歩き出す 道の向こうに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:28.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心色 Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:04.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无论晴天还是雨天 如果都有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:07.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就不需要天气预报了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:16.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天新的晨光中画下永不褪色的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:30.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,只用纸和彩铅 就能实现所有愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:38.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,每一天都仿佛重拾儿时的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:47.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愉快的季节告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:55.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,用涂鸦填满雪白的日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:04.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,十二色的调色板 画不尽的世界 永远烙在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 分享给100个我爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:12.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜花盛开的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无论晴天还是雨天 如果都有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就不需要天气预报了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:28.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,轻快地迈开脚步 道路的远方 是心中的彩虹
